title: 2020 Senate Races, WI Rep. Bryan Steil

description:
Guests: Gregory Korte, Bloomberg Senior National Political Correspondent, Calvin Schnure, Senior Economist at Nareit, Jack Kingston, Former Republican Georgia Congressman, and Trump 2020 campaign surrogate, Scott Bolden, Democratic strategist, and former D.C.
